// v2.9.124 — Time off simplified to a notification, not an approval workflow.
//   Submitting emails Ron (rl@tabsrq.org) + Pastor Dwain (pd@tabsrq.org) as To,
//   Ronel (ruys@thetabsarasota.org) as a courtesy Cc; Reply-To is the requester,
