//   every search hits PCO live). Gated to global-admin/staff/elders on both the
//   server and the client; hidden for everyone else and the endpoint stays
//   dormant + graceful (pco_not_configured) until the two PCO secrets are set on
//   THIS worker. Additive: 1 route, 1 backend fn, 1 card, 1 client fn, 1 flag.
//   No schema/auth/existing-feature change. Reuses .dir-row/.dir-act + calEsc();
//   no backticks or regex literals added inside the dashboardPage template.
// v2.9.115 — Added a staff-only Receipts launcher tile on Home (external link to the
//   Receipts app). Gated via USER_IS_STAFF (is_global_admin OR 'staff' role) so
